    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nIf the quickfix list contains only one entry, maps [q and ]q doesn't work to jump to that element. (No element before or after)\n\nError message:\n`E553: No more items`\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nIt would be great that **both** maps [q and ]q jump to the element, if the quickfix list contains only a single element.\n\nNVIM v0.12.0-dev-fd1e019",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-15T17:32:07Z",
